{"tid":217461,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"上網成日斷線求救","createTime":"2017-04-25T19:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T04:21:27.000Z","uid":32131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e16c7588c5f20774bb2f9025d53e66b3df965788","tid":217461,"uid":32131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:16:08.000Z","msg":"屋企上網近幾個月半個鐘至一個鐘斷一次線<br />\n每次10-30秒 <br />\n<br />\nlan部電腦係會顯示無連線<br />\nwifi係有信號但上唔到網<br />\n<br />\n試過果幾十秒間用speed test 測過 <br />\ndownload無問題 但係upload就得2mpbs<br />\n<br />\n打過去上網公司換過兩次wifi router<br />\n又有人黎試過信號係無問題<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打試過呢d情況解決左可以話我知點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家手機完全睇唔到波 一斷直情load唔番 <br />\n打打下機又斷好無引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885cf8e9a495d8cb697973db351d259b74b7c79e","tid":217461,"uid":17835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T23:28:32.000Z","msg":"如果你唔是光纖入屋，又唔係行pppoe 果d<br />\n直駁電腦試下用幾粒鐘睇下有冇事"},{"pid":"fcbc9489d0f5bbccd300e4ba1c7ab6f9beefa186","tid":217461,"uid":32131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你唔是光纖入屋，又唔係行pppoe 果d<br />\n直駁電腦試下用幾粒鐘睇下有冇事</blockquote><br />\n多謝你解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話就話係光纖<br />\n但係一條光纖分16個單位一齊用<br />\n我都唔知算唔算入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係直接用電腦 都會斷"},{"pid":"4dd52114a66abfb67b23c52d10e904072d4c80b7","tid":217461,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"router 好似有個setting <br />\n每隔幾耐就會離線，揀0就永不<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"a3c8542ea7b0e0ea14b4a6eb0003b093c77a5d8a","tid":217461,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:40:16.000Z","msg":"如果係用電話線上網8M果種<br />\n真係冇得救,因為電話線干擾太勁,落個雨都會出事<br />\n<br />\n以前苦主,後尾轉左光纖就冇事"},{"pid":"42c83cc1f979b2dd69f2ba26146334b8d847f285","tid":217461,"uid":32131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>router 好似有個setting <br />\n每隔幾耐就會離線，揀0就永不<br />\n<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n應該唔關事 我睇過應該無set到<br />\n之前用落都無問題<br />\n不過多謝你解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0521ec16ad74b5888f6b8766d0410c93ac73a691","tid":217461,"uid":32131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係用電話線上網8M果種<br />\n真係冇得救,因為電話線干擾太勁,落個雨都會出事<br />\n<br />\n以前苦主,後尾轉左光纖就冇事</blockquote><br />\n唔係電話線  係光纖不過唔係獨立線<br />\n但係落雨好似今日咁問題係嚴重左<br />\nlan線斷線果陣電腦係顯示連唔到線<br />\n個router d 燈都係1果粒息左<br />\nwan係長著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實會唔會係係入屋條光纖老化？<br />\n有無人有經驗？<br />\n<br />\n頭先打左去客戶服務講左成個鐘<br />\n死都唔肯同我睇入屋條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d55daa16cd8499369b4b337511775f940441f85","tid":217461,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"搬屋"}]}